    "However, it also comes with several ethical consequences.",
    "For instance, is it ethical for an AI crawler to scrape the internet for the latest news and then an LLM to use that data to craft automated news blog posts for a news site?",
    "Is it ethical for an AI with visual recognition to seek out for people in the crowd?",
    "How about for a company to use the intellectual property of others without their consent for Machine Learning?",
    "And those are only a few of the ethical dilemmas."
  ],
